title: How To Stop Being Impatient With Weightloss
itunes:title: How To Stop Being Impatient With Weightloss
description:
Get the Free Course here:

http://phit.click/freecourse

 

Are you impatient with your weightloss? A lot of people are. Most people who are impatient and making the process HARD. That's why they want it to be done.

 

Today I give you a three step process that helps you move out of impatience and into learning, growing, and just showing up each day doing the little things.
